(378, 1, 1, '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>\n<response>\n	<a key="cname">Kate Imbach</a>\n	<a key="cmail">kate@skyhookwireless.com</a>\n	<a key="cmessage">Dear Development Team,\r\nI''d like to tell you about an exciting new way to engage your iPhone users and keep them coming back to your music app with Skyhook''s Local Faves SDK http://www.skyhookwireless.com/localfaves/register. Skyhook powers the location technology on Apple products: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F624yzZ0Ysc.\r\nWith Local Faves you can easily add location-aware features like checking in, tagging, rankings, notifications and cool map views to any iPhone application. Local Faves saves you hours of development time, keeps your app content fresh and dynamic, all while driving deeper user engagement and viral growth of your app. Local Faves can be seamlessly integrated into your app. We just provide the underlying screens and infrastructure.\r\nFor instance a music app becomes less of a passive listening app and more playful when users can tag a song as their favorite, and share that with friends on Facebook, Twitter and Flickr. With map views you can see what the favorite song is at a particular venue and follow other users with the same music interests as you. Or a music creation app is much more fun when you can share it with the world and listen to the other melodies being created around you.\r\nEarly development partners will be featured on our new Local Faves webpage and will be invited to participate in media outreach.\r\n\r\nDownload our SDK here http://www.skyhookwireless.com/localfaves/register and start using Local Faves today.  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nKate Imbach\r\nSkyhook Wireless http://www.skyhookwireless.com \r\nkate@skyhookwireless.com\r\n617.938.3541</a>\n</response>', '2010-05-10 11:59:39', 0, NULL),
